{"tid":347711,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"[全民實驗]究竟茶包可唔可以趕曱甴？？","createTime":"2017-08-05T05:10:37.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-09T08:54:46.000Z","uid":25846,"like":18,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"088759f05214e405af3dae1c29861813570e6772","tid":347711,"uid":25846,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-05T05:10:37.000Z","msg":"話說早排老母係fb睇到<br />\n話將用完既茶包放係曱甴出沒嘅地方<br />\n曱甴就會唔出現，甚至被趕走<br />\n當初第一次聽，心諗<br />\non9啦邊有咁容易啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n點知之前有一期放咗一牌<br />\n啲曱甴真係冇晒！原本屋企好多曱甴<br />\n但同時我屋企都有連燈神獸嘅出現<br />\n所以我就將呢個結果歸因係連燈神獸出現所致<br />\n亦都叫老母收返啲茶包啦on9<br />\n<br />\n但係神奇嘅事就出現<br />\n當啲茶包被收起嘅時候<br />\n呢個就真係出返嚟！<br />\n所以我阿媽再唔信邪再放多次茶包出嚟<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/05/130643_5132caad9d905fbb9fb4bfb4f77220c9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F05%2F130643_5132caad9d905fbb9fb4bfb4f77220c9.jpg&h=114103d0&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/05/130700_9198985b806727f50e47ff2f0feface6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F05%2F130700_9198985b806727f50e47ff2f0feface6.jpg&h=02063e94&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n就好似咁<br />\n之後曱甴就真係又消失晒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n所以我想大家做個全民實驗<br />\n就係一齊試吓將用完嘅茶包(即沖完茶)<br />\n放喺曱甴出沒地方<br />\n再睇下曱甴出現嘅情況有冇改變<br />\n各位巴絲們快啲一齊試吓<br />\n可能幫到你驅走你一直以來好憎既曱甴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"60ee638b58a46634d11d685f31d714f1bbee3098","tid":347711,"uid":25846,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-05T05:12:03.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9d609a8056bcb672aaae66db9684a0d75dda1aad","tid":347711,"uid":72965,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-05T05:13:21.000Z","msg":"推，屋企飲水機位好多甲由<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fbadaff07745015548a959fe81deaf30dfe660d9","tid":347711,"uid":133256,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-05T05:25:58.000Z","msg":"咩茶?"},{"pid":"01f64dadf1b2e4ff0de4f74c5c9f9535804c079b","tid":347711,"uid":28624,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-05T05:37:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4ee4cb72f0c87c47eaf3a8a1c034050703330897","tid":347711,"uid":74380,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-05T05:37:58.000Z","msg":"係濕既都得定係要等佢乾左先得?"},{"pid":"65c8db76223fd081c7d4683ca2e433f7a3741963","tid":347711,"uid":25846,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-05T07:42:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>咩茶?</blockquote><br />\n我懷疑咩茶包都得，有待各位巴打做實驗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9d8b2c76dbd4cf5bd52cf360a0d379fd0ea525c8","tid":347711,"uid":25846,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-05T07:43:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>係濕既都得定係要等佢乾左先得?</blockquote><br />\n應該要乾咗先放<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d19c743989792cd6095d55b6c2f997a8df6193f0","tid":347711,"uid":31920,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-05T07:53:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>係濕既都得定係要等佢乾左先得?</blockquote><br />\n應該要乾咗先放<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n濕完再乾？定未濕過既乾？"},{"pid":"2a15be2373b9f2394b2376cf584b76e1f8d1e302","tid":347711,"uid":25846,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-05T08:14:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquo