rc=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"11fa36fb69da65dfd023061519ef3f4efca58d40","tid":347711,"uid":25846,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-05T15:48:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>甲由唔係會周屋走架咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />邊有固定位置</blockquote><br />\n之前主要係廚房，所以放左就消失哂，雖然有啲會喺廳出現"},{"pid":"50abfc7a21f52b2e0f20da6c16cf13f79a1fb2fd","tid":347711,"uid":25846,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-05T15:50:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>咩原理<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我覺得係因為啲曱甴會聞自己友嘅味黎搵食物，所以用完嘅茶包會吸左呢隻味，令到佢哋搵唔到自己嘅地盤<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n利申，鳩估"},{"pid":"82302eb3d535c923fd7ec309891165cbd75fb057","tid":347711,"uid":19068,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-05T16:46:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>咩原理<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我覺得係因為啲曱甴會聞自己友嘅味黎搵食物，所以用完嘅茶包會吸左呢隻味，令到佢哋搵唔到自己嘅地盤<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n利申，鳩估</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n不如咁講，甲由出現係啲濕臭環境，茶包吸味吸濕，環境乾爽咗，自然吸引唔到小強去嗰啲位。<br />\n<br />\n利申 我都係鳩估，晚晚同小強哥一齊訓"},{"pid":"2eed604065db214dd0f7084c5ebbc174c59554da","tid":347711,"uid":89449,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-05T16:48:06.000Z","msg":"推  返屋企試<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f4f0195a088ab66018c70d5875ad14cfe0a5e811","tid":347711,"uid":70832,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-05T16:48:49.000Z","msg":"屋企養左愛 ，甲由小左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2721ca9cc00c8498b816abcd2e444e36681f04c2","tid":347711,"uid":42586,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-05T17:11:50.000Z","msg":"茶葉有殺蟲水"},{"pid":"72e8209cfa6345c5e636cb26996031d0a7c4e055","tid":347711,"uid":25846,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-05T17:12:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>咩原理<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我覺得係因為啲曱甴會聞自己友嘅味黎搵食物，所以用完嘅茶包會吸左呢隻味，令到佢哋搵唔到自己嘅地盤<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n利申，鳩估</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n不如咁講，甲由出現係啲濕臭環境，茶包吸味吸濕，環境乾爽咗，自然吸引唔到小強去嗰啲位。<br />\n<br />\n利申 我都係鳩估，晚晚同小強哥一齊訓</blockquote><br />\n慘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 巴打快d試下"},{"pid":"81141f7379027f0b76349b537f450276d1ec1b7d","tid":347711,"uid":25846,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-05T17:13:02.000Z","msg":"如果有其他方法都可以攞出來討論下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n一齊做下實驗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9f97b76ed49351c51b5896d3ce6af0a1aeef2811","tid":347711,"uid":94090,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-05T17:13:41.000Z","msg":"lm"},{"pid":"180f4050398921ed591f86097aa240ff3a41e481","tid":347711,"uid":24698,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-05T17:15:00.000Z","msg":"試過有好多茶包放係櫃到 但都有小強"},{"pid":"55a870a49ebf4844e7dd35a649acc38a2a27d2b1","tid":347711,"uid":25846,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-05T18:00:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>試過有好多茶包放係櫃到 但都有小強</blockquote><br />\n要用過個d喎"},{"pid":"08ce868d20761a0cac7c016d152d330e4ce26dff","tid":347711,"uid":4525,"like":0,"dislike":0,"